data.description:
Architecturally Adorable Geo-Dome close to Leavenworth and Plain. Quiet, private feeling & a magically cozy place to feel like a kid again. A cabin in the woods with modern day amenities. 

Decks galore for entertaining. Hike up to the top which meets adjoining DNR land keep you fit & vitalized, snowboard or sled down, the little love it! 

40 X 24 ft 4 car Pole Barn garage with extended bays, no CC&R's or restrictions. Maybe run a business or store all your toys. You also have a green house, 2 stall barn and an extra 1 car garage up top for storage, think hobby farm. 

The bonus 500 Sqft garage below the main Dome has a separate driveway with 220V, loft, and heat. It was designed to have water & plumbing potentially. You could turn this into something for an extra income producing man cave/She-shed?!

Shared driveway & Artisan well with a gravity 3 bedroom septic. The water here is better than the bottled stuff. Long, hot showers or a deep soak in the jetted tub after a long day in the snow feels so nice. I use Frontier internet and have no issues with large downloads or service. 

I ran this as an Air bnb and Chelan county took away my rights to run a STR, though all tasks were completed and permitted. You may be able to re-apply in the future knowing everything is was permitted. I was late to re-apply because the work was delayed and my permit application was denied. 

Vacasa (my Short term rental management company) does do 30 day rentals and you would have no problem getting that type of business out here or a regular long term tenant.  It's a special gem and I'm selling because I live way too far to maintain it. 

I am a licensed real estate agent in Washington state. I would love to further discuss the details. Lets negotiate! *Jessica Garrett (360)-204-8090
